BusinessIns.name: Property Insurance

HealthIns.name: Individual Health
HealthIns.policy: Life Protection Plan Gold gives you extra  features for a very small yearly premium  so that you can protect your family's  future to ensure that they lead their  lives comfortably, without any financial  worries, even in your absence.  In the event of Accidental Death or  disability, the Plan shall provide for a  payment of Sum Assured to your nominee  as lump sum benefit.

MotorsIns.name: Vehicle
MotorsIns.policy: Motor insurance policy is also exclusively for the use of public sector. Motor car/commercial vehicles/motorcycle insurance policy provides coverage against accidental damage, fire, burglary, theft, malicious damage, riot & strike damage, damage due to natural calamities and third party liability arising due to Road Traffic Act or at Common Law and while in transit by road.
